citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
Section 2.126(b) - Access and inspection of records and property: A responsible adult shall be made available to
accompany APHIS officials during the inspection process.
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 4:51pm on
05/16/2016.
Licensee has moved and is no longer housing animals at the former address. Licensee shall notify the Region
office of this change, in writing, and submit it via certified mail.
